---
import '../styles/global.css';
const title = 'Legal Notice | Ads Calculator';
const description = 'Legal Notice of Ads Calculator. Information about the operator, terms of use, and legal disclaimer.';
---
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>{title}</title>
    <meta name="description" content={description} />
    <meta name="robots" content="index, follow" />
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://adsroicalc.com/legal" />
    <!-- Google AdSense -->
    <script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-8428748101355923" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  </head>
  <body class="min-h-screen bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-950 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">
    <header class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 py-4 px-6">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto flex justify-between items-center">
        <a href="/" class="font-bold text-xl">Ads <span class="text-blue-600 italic">Calculator</span></a>
        <a href="/" class="text-sm text-blue-600 hover:underline">← Back to calculator</a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-2 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Legal Notice</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-10">Last updated: April 2026</p>

      <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none space-y-8">

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">1. Website Operator</h2>
          <p>This website, <strong>adsroicalc.com</strong> (hereinafter "the Site"), is operated by the owner of Ads Calculator.</p>
          <p>Contact: <a href="mailto:hello@adsroicalc.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">hello@adsroicalc.com</a></p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">2. Purpose of the Site</h2>
          <p>Ads Calculator is a free online tool that enables users to calculate ROAS (Return on Ad Spend), ROI (Return on Investment), CPA (Cost per Acquisition), and the breakeven point for digital advertising campaigns. All calculations are performed client-side and no data is transmitted to our servers.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">3. Disclaimer of Liability</h2>
          <p>The results provided by this calculator are for <strong>informational and educational purposes only</strong>. They do not constitute financial, accounting, or legal advice. The operator accepts no responsibility for decisions made based on the data provided by the tool.</p>
          <p>While we strive to ensure accuracy, we cannot guarantee that the calculations are free from errors or that they reflect actual business outcomes.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">4. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p>All content on this site, including but not limited to text, graphics, code, and design, is the property of the site operator and is protected by applicable intellectual property laws. Reproduction without express permission is prohibited.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">5. External Links</h2>
          <p>This site may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the content or privacy practices of those external sites. Access to them is at the user's own risk.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">6. Governing Law</h2>
          <p>This Legal Notice is governed by applicable law. Any dispute arising from its interpretation shall be submitted to the competent courts.</p>
        </section>

      </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 py-8 px-6 text-center text-sm text-slate-500">
      <p>© 2026 Ads Calculator. All rights reserved. |
        <a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-blue-600 mx-2">Privacy Policy</a> |
        <a href="/legal" class="hover:text-blue-600 mx-2">Legal Notice</a> |
        <a href="/cookies" class="hover:text-blue-600 mx-2">Cookie Policy</a>
      </p>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
